choices.text:
BEEP turns into something unhealthy. In my country, i am too far from my family, friends, girlfriend, work, and with my economy being a huge disaster, i have to depend from my boy. (I love you so much). And this destroys me because i try to not talk to him because of his job, but we are at the phone like 20/7 because iam addicted to talk with him. And please i know are difficult, but please, you could give me an advice about my boy for be healthy.

(Im sorry about my english, i know its bad, and the last thing, i really apreciate your help, you are the one of the most important people for me, you talking is important for me.)

Hello my dear Maria. Im sorry the drama on Cuba is overwhelming. I believe everything happens for a reason. And it is overwhelming a reload of my life on my mind. About your problem, he is an adult and you cannot make his decisions or want a healthy relationship with you for his sake. He is a talented and popular artist. He has responsibilities in his own country and in ours. He loves you no doubt, and your love is not enough to change circumstances you cannot control. It takes two to make a partnership work no matter where you live as long as it’s necessary. Enjoy your life. You opened the world •for you. He will discover his world wherever he goes. He loves you even if you do not talk
